name: Barfiller
tagline: A simple jQuery plugin that gives you percentage-based animated bar filling...
body: Barfiller.js is a simple jQuery plugin that gives you percentage-based animated bar filling. All you have to do is set the data-percentage attribute to the percentage value that you want and then call Barfiller on the container element.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
